<p>
	John and Dave come to you on Tuesday for a special MGG this week. Discussing today&#39;s Apple Event&nbsp;<em>and</em> answering your questions, this show is bound to please and inform! In addition to all of today&#39;s Apple goodness, John and Dave answer your questions about how to stop iPhoto and PhotoStream from gobbling up all your bandwidth, how to share your new scanner on the network, how to rip Blu-Ray disks, and more!</p>
